title: Netherlands Manufacturing Production MoM
description: Manufacturing Production MoM in Netherlands increased to 0.50 percent in September from -1.70 percent in August of 2022. Manufacturing Production MoM in Netherlands averaged 0.16 percent from 1995 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 6.10 percent in January of 1999 and a record low of -8.10 percent in April of 2020. This page includes a chart with historical data for Netherlands Manufacturing Production MoM.
author: Statistics Netherlands
